{"id": 27, "name": "Texte de la commission sur la proposition de loi, apr\u00e8s engagement de la proc\u00e9dure acc\u00e9l\u00e9r\u00e9e, de M. Harold Huwart et plusieurs de ses coll\u00e8gues de simplification du droit de l'urbanisme et du logement (1240)., n\u00b0\u00a01378-A0", "url": "/dyn/17/amendements/1378/AN/27", "date": "2025-05-12", "status": "Rejet\u00e9", "proposed_by": [{"first_name": "St\u00e9phane", "last_name": "Peu", "party": "Gauche D\u00e9mocrate et R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Julien", "last_name": "Brugerolles", "party": "Gauche D\u00e9mocrate et R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Soumya", "last_name": "Bourouaha", "party": "Gauche D\u00e9mocrate et R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "\u00c9douard", "last_name": "B\u00e9nard", "party": "Gauche D\u00e9mocrate et R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Jean-Victor", "last_name": "Castor", "party": "Gauche D\u00e9mocrate et R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Elsa", "last_name": "Faucillon", "party": "Gauche D\u00e9mocrate et R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "\u00c9meline", "last_name": "K/Bidi", "party": "Gauche D\u00e9mocrate et R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Karine", "last_name": "Lebon", "party": "Gauche D\u00e9mocrate et R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Jean-Paul", "last_name": "Lecoq", "party": "Gauche D\u00e9mocrate et R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Fr\u00e9d\u00e9ric", "last_name": "Maillot", "party": "Gauche D\u00e9mocrate et R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Emmanuel", "last_name": "Maurel", "party": "Gauche D\u00e9mocrate et R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Yannick", "last_name": "Monnet", "party": "Gauche D\u00e9mocrate et R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Marcellin", "last_name": "Nadeau", "party": "Gauche D\u00e9mocrate et R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Mereana", "last_name": "Reid Arbelot", "party": "Gauche D\u00e9mocrate et R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Davy", "last_name": "Rimane", "party": "Gauche D\u00e9mocrate et R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Nicolas", "last_name": "Sansu", "party": "Gauche D\u00e9mocrate et R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Emmanuel", "last_name": "Tjibaou", "party": "Gauche D\u00e9mocrate et R\u00e9publicaine"}], "summary": "Compte tenu de l'ampleur des d\u00e9rogations aux r\u00e8gles d'urbanisme permises par l'article L.152-6 et en l'absence d'\u00e9tude d\u2019impact, les auteurs de l'amendement s\u2019interrogent sur l\u2019opportunit\u00e9 et sur les cons\u00e9quences de l\u2019extension de ces d\u00e9rogations \u00e0 l'ensemble des communes se caract\u00e9risant par un d\u00e9s\u00e9quilibre important entre l\u2019offre et la demande de logements. Sans doute aurait-il \u00e9t\u00e9 plus opportun de limiter ces d\u00e9rogations aux r\u00e8gles relatives \u00e0 la transformation \u00e0 usage principal d'habitation d'un immeuble existant par reconstruction, r\u00e9novation ou r\u00e9habilitation, afin de nous en tenir \u00e0 une mesure de facilitation la transformation de bureaux en logements."}